-module(main).
-export([main/1]).

% Generated by Mochi transpiler v0.10.35 (05628dc1c) on 2025-07-22 06:39 UTC

main(_) ->
    Data = [#{"a" => 1, "b" => 2}, #{"a" => 1, "b" => 1}, #{"a" => 0, "b" => 5}],
    Sorted = (fun() ->
        Pairs = [{#{"a" => maps:get("a", X), "b" => maps:get("b", X)}, X} ||
        X <- Data],
        SortedPairs = lists:sort(fun({K1,_},{K2,_}) -> K1 =< K2 end, Pairs),
        Values = [V || {_,V} <- SortedPairs],
        Values end)(),
    io:format("~p~n", [Sorted]).
